elements.description: You must insure your home for the full amount that it would cost to rebuild the home at today’s prices. This should include any home improvements on the site, for example a garage or swimming pool, as well as the costs to demolish and remove debris.

elements.label: What is the total cost to replace your contents at today's prices?
elements.description: General Contents are the things that you or your family keep in and around your home which include furniture, furnishing, rugs, electronic items, clothing and gardening equipment. You should insure your contents for the full amount that it would cost to replace them at today’s prices. When calculating your General Contents, do not include any items that you want to cover as Specified Portable Valuables.
